{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Coming to Early access this year!</h2>Battle of Orion 10 is a third person, action RPG that takes place in the year 2575 when humanity discover that they are not alone in the universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The story</h2>A hundred years have passed since the events on Cronos X transpired. The USN have not taken the warnings from Cronos to heed and is unprepared for the onslaught of the alien armada. Now, you must take point in fighting the brutal alien armada that is tearing through the outer rims and destroying the undefended human colonies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore worlds</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/extras/EXPLORE.jpg?t=1673434063\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight enemies</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/extras/FIGHT.jpg?t=1673434063\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fly between star systems and fight enemy space-craft</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/extras/SPACE_FLIGHT.jpg?t=1673434063\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft weapons, armor and upgrades</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/extras/CRAFT.jpg?t=1673434063\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Evolve your character</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/extras/EVOLVE.jpg?t=1673434063\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create your character</h2><br><strong>Four character classes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Warlock<br></li><li>Cyborg<br></li><li>Army veteran<br></li><li>Guardian</li></ul><br><strong>Four race classes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Centurion<br></li><li>Mercurian<br></li><li>Lunar / Earther<br></li><li>Venucian</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Steam achievements</h2>Earn Steam achievements as you advance through the game, solving missions and learning about Cronos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The story</h2>Humans have explored many star systems and made countless colonies in the bordering star systems. You have been in the service of the USN black ops for many decades (United Sol Nation) and has been sent to investigate an emergency signal sent by one of the colonies in the rim-worlds.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1673434063","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/page.bg.jpg?t=1673434063","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1673434063","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252380/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1673434063","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"The game contain violence in the form of armed combat between the player character and enemies - both melee and ranged fighting. There is blood-splatter and other particle effects.\r\n\r\nSome characters in the game are dressed in a way that may appear sexual or revealing."},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Coming to Early access this year!</h2>Battle of Orion 10 is a third person, action RPG that takes place in the year 2575 when humanity discover that they are not alone in the universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The story</h2>A hundred years have passed since the events on Cronos X transpired. The USN have not taken the warnings from Cronos to heed and is unprepared for the onslaught of the alien armada. Now, you must take point in fighting the brutal alien armada that is tearing through the outer rims and destroying the undefended human colonies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore worlds</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"ht